                        Our Products
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed" style="font-weight: 300;">
                        Discover our comprehensive range of precision machinery and industrial solutions, engineered for excellence.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 产品分类和列表 -->
